N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 1015.11 - Gratuities to public employees

State Regulations

No attorney shall give any gift or gratuity to any
employee of any court or other governmental agency with which such attorney has
had or is likely to have any professional or official transaction. Notes
